    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_1201420734169313165.png",
                "id": "talent31301",
                "key": "Flowing Eddies",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Flowing Eddies"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>. If this character has not yet gained <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Pers Timer</span>, they will gain<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> Pers Timer</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Pers Timer</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">For every 1 card you draw: </span>This card will gain 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Pressure Level</span>.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">When the attached character uses Pressurized Floe: </span>If <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Pressure Level</span> is at least 2, cancel this effect, and the Skill costs 1 less Elemental Die. If, after the Skill is finalized, the Pressure Level is at least 4, deal 2 additional<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/3402e8d6f5344bbe19aaff03729bbdee_1017195788770685692.png",
                "id": "talent23619",
                "key": "Pressurized Floe",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pressurized Floe"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>. Attaches <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Subnautical Hunter Mode</span> to this character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Subnautical Hunter Mode</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">After you draw 3 cards:</span> Grants 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Shield </span>point to defend the attached character. (Can stack. Max 2 points.)<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">After the attached character uses a Normal Attack or Elemental Skill: </span>Place up to 2 cards with the highest Elemental Dice Cost in your Hand at the bottom of your deck, then draw the same number of cards.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/5689131a4a2251f39d27b6b0a2e5c106_1807766230622883561.png",
                "id": "talent88487",
                "key": "Shadowhunter's Ambush",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Shadowhunter's Ambush"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Cryo and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_6787059211547974912.png",
                "id": "talent31925",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Shield</span></strong></p><p>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong></p><p>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds) </span>-1.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_5301069784114566325.png",
                "id": "talent55581",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
